metadata.description:
"Wonder" written and performed by J. Adair. "Wonder" talks about a past lover and the experiences that led to an unexpected break up.   Artwork for the song was created by Dylan Gill Art. 

You're purchasing non-commercial rights of J. Adair x Dylan Gill Art “Wonder”.

(You can resell this NFT with same rights, but you will lose your rights when you are no longer the owner of this NFT!) This is just like buying your own personal vinyl copy, except in a Digital format. You own it & you can resell it just like a used / physical record or CD!
